---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const values = [
  'Transparent business practices',
  'Consistent quality',
  'Lasting relationships through trust, reliability, and continuous improvement',
];
---
<Layout
  title="About S R Group"
  description="S R Group is a family-owned chemical manufacturing group based in Chhatral GIDC, Gujarat, established in 1997 by the late Shri Ramanbhai Patel and his sons."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About S R Group</span>
      <h1>Built on Trust.<br/>Driven by Family Values.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="rule-dashed container-rule" />

  <section class="section story">
    <div class="container story-grid">
      <div class="story-copy">
        <p>
          S R Group is a family-owned chemical manufacturing group based in Chhatral GIDC, Gujarat.
        </p>
        <p>
          Established in 1997 by the late Shri Ramanbhai Patel together with his sons, Nilesh Patel and Krushi Patel,
          the company was founded with a clear vision — to build a business rooted in integrity, dependable products,
          and lasting customer relationships.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the years, S R Group has grown into three manufacturing companies —<br/>
          S R Industries, S R Plast, and S R Polymers — manufacturing industrial chemicals, distilled solvents,
          and unsaturated polyester resins for customers across India while steadily expanding into international markets.
        </p>
        <p>
          With a strong foundation built over nearly three decades, Henil Patel and Kushal Patel represent the next
          generation of S R Group, carrying forward its legacy by combining the company's core values with a modern
          approach to manufacturing and innovation.
        </p>
        <p>
          As the business continues to evolve, the principles on which it was founded remain unchanged.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="story-values">
        <span class="eyebrow">We Believe In</span>
        <ul>
          {values.map((v) => <li>{v}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { padding: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-4); }
  .page-hero .eyebrow { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .page-hero h1 { max-width: 780px; }

  .container-rule { max-width: var(--container); margin: 0 auto; }

  .story { padding-top: var(--space-6); }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-copy { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); max-width: 620px; }

  .story-copy p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-align: justify;
    text-justify: inter-word;
    hyphens: auto;
  }

  .story-copy p:first-child {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .story-values {
    position: sticky;
    top: 110px;
    border-left: 1px dashed var(--gold);
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
  }

  .story-values .eyebrow { margin-bottom: var(--space-3); display: block; }

  .story-values ul { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }

  .story-values li {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.4;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .story-values li:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); }
    .story-values {
      position: static;
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px dashed var(--gold);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: var(--space-3);
    }
  }
</style>
